And if you'd read the posts, Dark One didn't eat her, Oblitertron jerked her 
away. She did respond and everything, but I didn't know about the fire shield.

Anyways, since this has to do with Logo's char, lets let her decide. Whatever 
she says (Who has Squizzy: Dark One or Arcangel) will be final then.

::The Oblitercons/DevilDuer::

DevilDuer laughs as he gets the Lavacon's transmission. "We captured? We 
didn't capture anyone! A bot crashed, on Alliance territory, and these 
Maximals attacked, and nearly killed her! The Maximals are attacking, not us, 
we're simply defending."

He yells as flames cover him, jumping backwards, his body flaming.

"Dangit, get otta our territory!" he yells, firing his stun gun at Decadel, 
the weapon getting low on energy.
